{"article_id":"sUX79s7sBz8JkdFC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Key government surveillance powers under the Patriot Act were set to expire Monday","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"after Republican leaders were unable to surmount the objections of Sen. Rand Paul ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"sending Congress careening past a midnight deadline .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"All sides said","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"the situation would soon be fixed","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"- even Mr. Paul acknowledged","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"he can delay matters for only a couple of days -","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"but for now , the U.S. government no longer can obtain wiretaps","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that follow terrorists from phone to phone ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"nor can it compel businesses to turn over customers ' documents or records","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"without going through the traditional warrant process .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Even as he staged his lonely fight ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Mr. Paul acknowledged","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"it was futile in the long run .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"\" The Patriot Act will expire tonight .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"It will only be temporary .","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"They will ultimately get their way , \"","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"said the Kentucky Republican ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"underscoring the limits of his powers of objection ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"which can push matters until Wednesday at the latest .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"In the interim , the National Security Agency won ' t be allowed to collect mass amounts of new telephone metadata ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"putting at least a temporary crimp in the program","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"revealed two years ago by former government contractor Edward Snowden .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"The expiration was a black eye for the Senate and particularly for Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , Mr. Paul ' s fellow Kentucky Republican ,","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"who supports the full extension of all Patriot Act powers ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"including bulk collection .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"But Mr. McConnell badly miscalculated the strength of his own hand","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"and bungled the schedule ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"leaving Mr. Paul with enough power","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"to push the powers to the brink of expiration .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"The Senate ' s inept handling of the issue stood in stark contrast to the House ,","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"which overwhelmingly passed a bipartisan rewrite of the Patriot Act several weeks ago in the form of the USA Freedom Act .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"That bill would fully extend two powers","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"- the wiretap provision and another section","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"that allows investigators to target \" lone wolf \" terrorists -","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"while curtailing the records collection provision .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"Under the USA Freedom Act , investigators could go after the records of individuals ,","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"but the government ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"including the NSA ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"no longer could demand Americans ' data in bulk .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"House leaders watched with dismay","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"as their work was squandered by Senate dithering .","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"\" Anyone","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"who is satisfied with letting this critical intelligence capability go dark","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"isn ' t taking the terrorist threat seriously .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"I ' d urge the Senate to pass the bipartisan USA Freedom Act ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"and do so expeditiously , \"","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"said House Speaker John A. Boehner , Ohio Republican .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"President Obama has said","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"he was ready to sign the House bill ,","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"and the White House urged the Senate repeatedly to act in recent days .","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"Mr. McConnell even tried to reverse himself late Sunday .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"After leading a filibuster against the USA Freedom Act a week ago ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"he asked for a do-over","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"and tried to speed the bill through the Senate before the midnight deadline .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"\" It ' s not ideal","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"but , along with votes on some modest amendments","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"that attempt to ensure","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"the program can actually work","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"as promised ,","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"it ' s now the only realistic way forward , \"","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Mr. McConnell said .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"The Senate voted 77-17 to end Mr. McConnell ' s earlier filibuster .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"But he had left too little time for quick action","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"and Mr. Paul ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"using the rules of the Senate","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"that give any senator immense powers","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"to delay action ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"pounced .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"\" This is a debate over the Bill of Rights .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"This is a debate over the Fourth Amendment .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"This is a debate over your right","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"to be left alone , \"","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"Mr. Paul is seeking the Republican presidential nomination next year .","depth":3},{"id":75,"text":"Some of his supporters ,","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"wearing red \" Stand with Rand \" T-shirts ,","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"packed the viewing galleries ,","depth":5},{"id":78,"text":"underscoring the weighty politics","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"involved .","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"Mr. Paul ' s fellow Republicans tried to silence him .","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"Sen. John McCain of Arizona , a supporter of the Patriot Act ' s powers , accused Mr. Paul of not knowing the Senate ' s rules .","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"Mr. Paul prevailed , however ,","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"and earned his speaking time .","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"Three powers of the Patriot Act ,","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"passed in the days immediately after the Sept. 11 , 2001 , terrorist attacks ,","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"are deemed so controversial","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"that they are regularly set to expire","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"- or \" sunset \" -","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"unless Congress agrees to continue them :","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"the wiretap powers , a provision","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"that allows investigators to target \" lone-wolf \" terrorists ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"and the records collection powers .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"The provisions have been extended several times ,","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"but after Mr. Snowden ' s revelations","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"that the NSA was collecting all Americans ' phone metadata","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"- the numbers , dates and durations of phone calls -","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"the records collection powers ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"contained in Section 215 of the Patriot Act ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"became a major flashpoint .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"In some ways , it ' s unusual that the program has produced such heat .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"There have never been any proven abuses of the program ,","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"and bulk collection has not foiled any terrorist plots .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"But NSA backers such as Mr. McConnell insist","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"that the program is carefully crafted","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"and is critical at a time","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"when the terrorist threat is expanding .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"He doubted the administration ' s assurances","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"that it can rely on private companies","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"to collect and store the data","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"for investigators to peruse","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"if they believe","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"they have a terrorist suspect .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":225,"left":186,"right":224,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":152,"right":185,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":135,"right":151,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":115,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":0,"right":114,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":122,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":120,"right":121,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":120,"left":118,"right":119,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":118,"left":3,"right":117,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":117,"left":4,"right":116,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":119,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":124,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":11,"right":123,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":132,"left":129,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":127,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent